      "content": "wait really?? i thought tremor was just something that happened when you first start the meds. and stop taking it completely?? i'm scared to just quit cold turkey. is the charcoal thing actually gonna work for me tho? i have some in my cabinet, i dont want to have to drive to the er if i dont have to.",
